steps.name: user navigates to tutorials ninja website and verify that the title is "Your Store"
user selects Laptops & Notebooks  From top menu
user selects Show All Laptops & Notebooks From dropdown menu
user finds the Macbook item and click ADD TO CART
user clicks Cart Button and clicks View Cart From the top side
user clicks on Checkout button
In Checkout Options user selects Guest Checkout and clicks Continue
In Billing details user enters all mandatory fields and Continue
user adds In Payment Method and adds a comment
In Payment Method, user selects Agree radio button and Continue
user Verify that "Warning: Payment method required!" and closes the browser
